401 inline float getManhattanDistanceTo(float inX, float inY)
402 {
403 if (leftX < inX && inX <= rightX && bottomY < inY && inY <= topY)
404 {
405 return 0;
406 }
407 if (leftX < inX && inX <= rightX)
408 {
409 return std::min(std::fabs(inY - topY), std::fabs(inY - bottomY));
410 }
411 if (bottomY < inY && inY <= topY)
412 {
413 return std::min(std::fabs(inX - leftX), std::fabs(inX - rightX));
414 }
415 return std::min(std::fabs(inX - leftX), std::fabs(inX - rightX)) +
416 std::min(std::fabs(inY - topY), std::fabs(inY - bottomY));
417 }

580 inline float getRealUtilizationRate()
581 {
582 if (cells.size())
583 {
584 std::vector<DesignInfo::DesignCell *> cellVec;
585 cellVec.clear();
586 for (auto cell : cells)
587 {
588 cellVec.push_back(cell);
589 }
590 if (cellVec[0]->isLUT())
591 {
592 float tmputilization = 0;
593 for (auto cell : cells)
594 {
595 if (cell->isLUT6())
596 tmputilization += 2.0;
597 else
598 tmputilization += 1;
599 }
600 return (float)tmputilization / capacity;
601 }
602 else
603 {
604 return getUtilizationRate();
605 }
606 }
607 return 0;
608 }

1738 class PlacementNet
1739 {
1740 public:
1748 PlacementNet(DesignInfo::DesignNet *designNet, int id, std::vector<PlacementUnit *> &cellId2PlacementUnitVec,
1749 PlacementInfo *placementInfo)
1750 : designNet(designNet), id(id), placementInfo(placementInfo)
1751 {
1752 unitsOfNetPins.clear();
1753 unitsOfDriverPins.clear();
1754 unitsOfPinsBeDriven.clear();
1755 PUSet.clear();
1756 for (DesignInfo::DesignPin *curPin : designNet->getPins())
1757 {
1758 PlacementUnit *tmpPU = cellId2PlacementUnitVec[curPin->getCell()->getElementIdInType()];
1759 unitsOfNetPins.push_back(tmpPU);
1760 PUSet.insert(tmpPU);
1761
1762 if (curPin->isOutputPort())
1763 {
1764 unitsOfDriverPins.push_back(tmpPU);
1765 }
1766 else
1767 {
1768 unitsOfPinsBeDriven.push_back(tmpPU);
1769 }
1770
1771 if (tmpPU->getType() == PlacementUnitType_UnpackedCell)
1772 {
1773 pinOffset tmpPinOffset = pinOffset(curPin->getOffsetXInCell(), curPin->getOffsetYInCell());
1774 pinOffsetsInUnit.push_back(tmpPinOffset);
1775 }
1776 else if (tmpPU->getType() == PlacementUnitType_Macro)
1777 {
1778 PlacementMacro *tmpM = dynamic_cast<PlacementMacro *>(tmpPU);
1779 assert(tmpM);
1780 pinOffset tmpPinOffset =
1781 pinOffset(curPin->getOffsetXInCell() + tmpM->getCellOffsetXInMacro(curPin->getCell()),
1782 curPin->getOffsetYInCell() + tmpM->getCellOffsetYInMacro(curPin->getCell()));
1783 pinOffsetsInUnit.push_back(tmpPinOffset);
1784 }
1785 }
1786 leftPuId = rightPuId = topPuId = bottomPuId = -1;
1787 }
1788 ~PlacementNet()
1789 {
1790 }

1868 inline bool updateNetBounds(bool updateX, bool updateY)
1869 {
1870 if (updateX)
1871 {
1872 leftPUX = 1e5;
1873 rightPUX = -1e5;
1874 leftPinX = 1e5;
1875 rightPinX = -1e5;
1876 for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
1877 {
1878 auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
1879 auto tmpPUId = tmpPU->getId();
1880 auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
1881 float cellX = tmpPU->X();
1882 float pinX = tmpPU->X() + tmpPinOffset.x;
1883 if (pinX < leftPinX)
1884 {
1885 leftPinX = pinX;
1886 leftPUX = cellX;
1887 leftPuId = tmpPUId;
1888 leftPinId_net = pinId_net;
1889 }
1890 if (pinX > rightPinX)
1891 {
1892 rightPinX = pinX;
1893 rightPUX = cellX;
1894 rightPuId = tmpPUId;
1895 rightPinId_net = pinId_net;
1896 }
1897 }
1898 }
1899 if (updateY)
1900 {
1901 topPUY = -1e5;
1902 bottomPUY = 1e5;
1903 topPinY = -1e5;
1904 bottomPinY = 1e5;
1905 for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
1906 {
1907 auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
1908 auto tmpPUId = tmpPU->getId();
1909 auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
1910 float cellY = tmpPU->Y();
1911 float pinY = tmpPU->Y() + tmpPinOffset.y;
1912 if (pinY < bottomPinY)
1913 {
1914 bottomPinY = pinY;
1915 bottomPUY = cellY;
1916 bottomPuId = tmpPUId;
1917 bottomPinId_net = pinId_net;
1918 }
1919 if (pinY > topPinY)
1920 {
1921 topPinY = pinY;
1922 topPUY = cellY;
1923 topPuId = tmpPUId;
1924 topPinId_net = pinId_net;
1925 }
1926 }
1927 }
1928 return (updateX && (leftPuId != rightPuId)) || (updateY && (topPuId != bottomPuId));
1929 }

1938 inline float getHPWL(float y2xRatio)
1939 {
1940 return std::fabs(rightPinX - leftPinX) + y2xRatio * std::fabs(topPinY - bottomPinY);
1941 }
1942
1955 inline float getNewHPWLByTrying(PlacementUnit *curPU, double targetPUX, double targetPUY, float y2xRatio) const
1956 {
1957 float tmp_leftX = 1e5;
1958 float tmp_rightX = -1e5;
1959 float tmp_topY = -1e5;
1960 float tmp_bottomY = 1e5;
1961
1962 for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
1963 {
1964 auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
1965 auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
1966 float pinX;
1967 if (tmpPU == curPU)
1968 {
1969 pinX = targetPUX + tmpPinOffset.x;
1970 }
1971 else
1972 {
1973 pinX = tmpPU->X() + tmpPinOffset.x;
1974 }
1975 if (pinX < tmp_leftX)
1976 {
1977 tmp_leftX = pinX;
1978 }
1979 if (pinX > tmp_rightX)
1980 {
1981 tmp_rightX = pinX;
1982 }
1983 }
1984 for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
1985 {
1986 auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
1987 auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
1988 float pinY;
1989 if (tmpPU == curPU)
1990 {
1991 pinY = targetPUY + tmpPinOffset.y;
1992 }
1993 else
1994 {
1995 pinY = tmpPU->Y() + tmpPinOffset.y;
1996 }
1997 if (pinY < tmp_bottomY)
1998 {
1999 tmp_bottomY = pinY;
2000 }
2001 if (pinY > tmp_topY)
2002 {
2003 tmp_topY = pinY;
2004 }
2005 }
2006
2007 int A_ClockRegionY, A_ClockRegionX;
2008 placementInfo->getDeviceInfo()->getClockRegionByLocation(tmp_rightX, tmp_bottomY, A_ClockRegionX,
2009 A_ClockRegionY);
2010 std::pair<int, int> A_ClockLocYX(A_ClockRegionY, A_ClockRegionX);
2011
2012 int B_cellClockRegionY, B_cellClockRegionX;
2013 placementInfo->getDeviceInfo()->getClockRegionByLocation(tmp_leftX, tmp_topY, B_cellClockRegionX,
2014 B_cellClockRegionY);
2015 std::pair<int, int> B_ClockLocYX(B_cellClockRegionY, B_cellClockRegionX);
2016
2017 float clockRegionOverhead = 0;
2018 if (B_ClockLocYX != A_ClockLocYX)
2019 {
2020 clockRegionOverhead = std::abs(B_cellClockRegionX - A_ClockRegionX) * 15 +
2021 std::abs(B_cellClockRegionY - A_ClockRegionY) * 6;
2022 }
2023
2024 return std::fabs(tmp_rightX - tmp_leftX) + y2xRatio * std::fabs(tmp_topY - tmp_bottomY) +
2025 clockRegionOverhead;
2026 }

2047 inline void updateBound2BoundNetWeight(std::vector<Eigen::Triplet<float>> &objectiveMatrixTripletList,
2048 std::vector<float> &objectiveMatrixDiag,
2049 Eigen::VectorXd &objectiveVector, float generalWeight, float y2xRatio,
2050 bool updateX, bool updateY)
2051 {
2052 assert(updateX ^ updateY);
2053 if (pinOffsetsInUnit.size() <= 1)
2054 return;
2055 float w = 2.0 * generalWeight / (float)(pinOffsetsInUnit.size() - 1);
2056 int nPins = pinOffsetsInUnit.size();
2057
2058 // adopt netDegree Weight from RippeFPGA
2059 if (nPins < 10)
2060 w *= 1.00;
2061 else if (nPins < 20)
2062 w *= 1.2;
2063 else if (nPins < 50)
2064 w *= 1.6;
2065 else if (nPins < 100)
2066 w *= 1.8;
2067 else if (nPins < 200)
2068 w *= 2.1;
2069 else
2070 w *= 2.5;
2071
2072 w *= designNet->getOverallEnhanceRatio();
2073 if (updateX)
2074 {
2075 // add net between left node and right node
2076 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, leftPuId, rightPuId,
2077 leftPUX, rightPUX, pinOffsetsInUnit[leftPinId_net].x, pinOffsetsInUnit[rightPinId_net].x,
2078 !unitsOfNetPins[leftPinId_net]->isFixed(), !unitsOfNetPins[rightPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2079 designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(leftPinId_net, rightPinId_net) * w /
2080 std::max(minDist, rightPinX - leftPinX));
2081
2082 // add net between internal node and left/right node
2083 for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
2084 {
2085 auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
2086 auto tmpPUId = tmpPU->getId();
2087 auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
2088 float curX = tmpPU->X();
2089 bool movable = !tmpPU->isFixed();
2090 if (pinId_net != leftPinId_net && pinId_net != rightPinId_net)
2091 {
2092 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, tmpPUId, leftPuId,
2093 curX, leftPUX, tmpPinOffset.x, pinOffsetsInUnit[leftPinId_net].x, movable,
2094 !unitsOfNetPins[leftPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2095 designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(pinId_net, leftPinId_net) * w /
2096 std::max(minDist, (curX + tmpPinOffset.x) - leftPinX));
2097 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, tmpPUId, rightPuId,
2098 curX, rightPUX, tmpPinOffset.x, pinOffsetsInUnit[rightPinId_net].x, movable,
2099 !unitsOfNetPins[rightPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2100 designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(pinId_net, rightPinId_net) * w /
2101 std::max(minDist, rightPinX - (curX + tmpPinOffset.x)));
2102 }
2103 }
2104 }
2105 if (updateY)
2106 {
2107 w *= y2xRatio;
2108
2109 // add net between top node and bottom node
2110 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, bottomPuId, topPuId,
2111 bottomPUY, topPUY, pinOffsetsInUnit[bottomPinId_net].y, pinOffsetsInUnit[topPinId_net].y,
2112 !unitsOfNetPins[bottomPinId_net]->isFixed(), !unitsOfNetPins[topPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2113 designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(topPinId_net, bottomPinId_net) * w /
2114 std::max(minDist, topPinY - bottomPinY));
2115
2116 // add net between internal node and top/bottom node
2117 for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
2118 {
2119 auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
2120 auto tmpPUId = tmpPU->getId();
2121 auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
2122 float curY = tmpPU->Y();
2123 bool movable = !tmpPU->isFixed();
2124 if (pinId_net != topPinId_net && pinId_net != bottomPinId_net)
2125 {
2126 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, tmpPUId, bottomPuId,
2127 curY, bottomPUY, tmpPinOffset.y, pinOffsetsInUnit[bottomPinId_net].y, movable,
2128 !unitsOfNetPins[bottomPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2129 designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(pinId_net, bottomPinId_net) * w /
2130 std::max(minDist, (curY + tmpPinOffset.y) - bottomPinY));
2131 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, tmpPUId, topPuId,
2132 curY, topPUY, tmpPinOffset.y, pinOffsetsInUnit[topPinId_net].y, movable,
2133 !unitsOfNetPins[topPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2134 designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(pinId_net, topPinId_net) * w /
2135 std::max(minDist, topPinY - (curY + tmpPinOffset.y)));
2136 }
2137 }
2138 }
2139 }
2140
2141 inline void addPseudoNet_enhancePin2Pin(std::vector<Eigen::Triplet<float>> &objectiveMatrixTripletList,
2142 std::vector<float> &objectiveMatrixDiag,
2143 Eigen::VectorXd &objectiveVector, float generalWeight, float y2xRatio,
2144 bool updateX, bool updateY, int PUIdA, int PUIdB, int pinIdA_net,
2145 int pinIdB_net)
2146 {
2147 float w = generalWeight;
2148
2149 if (updateX)
2150 {
2151 // add net between left node and right node
2152 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, PUIdA, PUIdB,
2153 unitsOfNetPins[pinIdA_net]->X(), unitsOfNetPins[pinIdB_net]->X(),
2154 pinOffsetsInUnit[pinIdA_net].x, pinOffsetsInUnit[pinIdB_net].x,
2155 !unitsOfNetPins[pinIdA_net]->isFixed(), !unitsOfNetPins[pinIdB_net]->isFixed(), w);
2156 }
2157 if (updateY)
2158 {
2159 w *= y2xRatio;
2160
2161 // add net between top node and bottom node
2162 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, PUIdA, PUIdB,
2163 unitsOfNetPins[pinIdA_net]->Y(), unitsOfNetPins[pinIdB_net]->Y(),

2191 inline void addB2BNet(std::vector<Eigen::Triplet<float>> &objectiveMatrixTripletList,
2192 std::vector<float> &objectiveMatrixDiag, Eigen::VectorXd &objectiveVector, int puId0,
2193 int puId1, float pos0, float pos1, float pinOffset0, float pinOffset1, bool movable0,
2194 bool movable1, float w)
2195 {
2196 // min_x 0.5 * x'Px + q'x
2197 // s.t. l <= Ax <= u
2198 if (puId0 == puId1)
2199 return;
2200 if (movable0 && movable1)
2201 {
2202 // x0^2 + x1^2 - 2x0x1 + 2(x0c-x1c)x0 + 2(x1c-x0c)x1
2203 // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId0, puId0, w));
2204 // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId1, puId1, w));
2205 objectiveMatrixDiag[puId0] += w;
2206 objectiveMatrixDiag[puId1] += w;
2207 objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId0, puId1, -w));
2208 objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId1, puId0, -w));
2209 if (fabs(pinOffset0) > eps || fabs(pinOffset1) > eps)
2210 {
2211 // 2(x0c-x1c)x0 + 2(x1c-x0c)x1
2212 objectiveVector[puId0] += w * (pinOffset0 - pinOffset1);
2213 objectiveVector[puId1] += w * (pinOffset1 - pinOffset0);
2214 }
2215 }
2216 else if (movable0)
2217 {
2218 // x0^2 - 2x0x1 + 2(x0c-x1c)x0
2219 // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId0, puId0, w));
2220 objectiveMatrixDiag[puId0] += w;
2221 objectiveVector[puId0] += -w * pos1;
2222 if (fabs(pinOffset0) > eps || fabs(pinOffset1) > eps)
2223 {
2224 // 2(x0c-x1c)x0
2225 objectiveVector[puId0] += w * (pinOffset0 - pinOffset1);
2226 }
2227 }
2228 else if (movable1)
2229 {
2230 // x1^2 - 2x0x1 + 2(x1c-x0c)x1
2231 // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId1, puId1, w));
2232 objectiveMatrixDiag[puId1] += w;
2233 objectiveVector[puId1] += -w * pos0;
2234 if (fabs(pinOffset0) > eps || fabs(pinOffset1) > eps)
2235 {
2236 // 2(x1c-x0c)x1
2237 objectiveVector[puId1] += w * (pinOffset1 - pinOffset0);
2238 }

2846 inline std::vector<DesignInfo::DesignCell *> *
2847 findNeiborLUTFFsFromBinGrid(DesignInfo::DesignCell *curCell, float displacementUpperbound, int minNumNeighbor = 10)
2848 {
2849 // please note that the input DesignCell is only used to find the corresponding binGrid for site search.
2850 bool findLUT = curCell->isLUT();
2851 float targetX = cellId2location[curCell->getCellId()].X;
2852 float targetY = cellId2location[curCell->getCellId()].Y;
2853 std::vector<DesignInfo::DesignCell *> *res = new std::vector<DesignInfo::DesignCell *>();
2854 res->clear();
2855
2856 int binIdX, binIdY;
2857 getGridXY(targetX, targetY, binIdX, binIdY);
2858
2859 assert(binIdY >= 0);
2860 assert((unsigned int)binIdY < LUTFFBinGrid.size());
2861 assert(binIdX >= 0);
2862 assert((unsigned int)binIdX < LUTFFBinGrid[binIdY].size());
2863 assert(LUTFFBinGrid[binIdY][binIdX]->inRange(targetX, targetY));
2864
2865 std::queue<std::pair<int, int>> binXYqueue;
2866 std::set<std::pair<int, int>> reachedBinXYs;
2867 binXYqueue.emplace(binIdX, binIdY);
2868 reachedBinXYs.emplace(binIdX, binIdY);
2869
2870 bool findItself = false;
2871
2872 while (binXYqueue.size() > 0)
2873 {
2874 std::pair<int, int> curXY = binXYqueue.front();
2875 binXYqueue.pop();
2876 int curbinIdX = curXY.first, curbinIdY = curXY.second;
2877
2878 PlacementInfo::PlacementBinInfo *curBin = LUTFFBinGrid[curbinIdY][curbinIdX];
2879 float bin2TargetXYDistance = curBin->getManhattanDistanceTo(targetX, targetY);
2880 if (bin2TargetXYDistance > displacementUpperbound)
2881 continue;
2882 for (auto tmpCell : curBin->getCells())
2883 {
2884 if ((tmpCell->isLUT() && findLUT) || (tmpCell->isFF() && !findLUT))
2885 {
2886 float tmpX = cellId2location[tmpCell->getCellId()].X;
2887 float tmpY = cellId2location[tmpCell->getCellId()].Y;
2888 float tmpPUDis = fabs(targetX - tmpX) + y2xRatio * fabs(targetY - tmpY);
2889 if (tmpPUDis <= displacementUpperbound)
2890 {
2891 if (tmpCell == curCell)
2892 {
2893 findItself = true;
2894 }
2895 res->push_back(tmpCell);
2896 }
2897 }
2898 }
2899 assert(findItself);
2900 for (int nextY = curbinIdY - 1; nextY <= curbinIdY + 1; nextY++)
2901 {
2902 for (int nextX = curbinIdX - 1; nextX <= curbinIdX + 1; nextX++)
2903 {
2904 if (!(nextY >= 0))
2905 continue;
2906 if (!((unsigned int)nextY < LUTFFBinGrid.size()))
2907 continue;
2908 if (!(nextX >= 0))
2909 continue;
2910 if (!((unsigned int)nextX < LUTFFBinGrid[binIdY].size()))
2911 continue;
2912 PlacementInfo::PlacementBinInfo *nextBin = LUTFFBinGrid[nextY][nextX];
2913 float nextBin2TargetXYDistance = nextBin->getManhattanDistanceTo(targetX, targetY);
2914 if (nextBin2TargetXYDistance > displacementUpperbound)
2915 continue;
2916 std::pair<int, int> nextXY(nextX, nextY);
2917 if (reachedBinXYs.find(nextXY) == reachedBinXYs.end())
2918 {
2919 reachedBinXYs.insert(nextXY);
2920 binXYqueue.push(nextXY);
2921 }
2922 }
2923 }
2924 }
2925
2926 assert(findItself);
2927 return res;
2928 }

3280 inline bool isLegalLocation(DesignInfo::DesignCell *curCell, float targetX, float targetY)
3281 {

3283
3284 if (curPU->getType() == PlacementUnitType_UnpackedCell)
3285 {
3286 float fX = targetX;
3287 float fY = targetY;
3288 fX = std::max(globalMinX + eps, (std::min(fX, globalMaxX - eps)));
3289 fY = std::max(globalMinY + eps, (std::min(fY, globalMaxY - eps)));
3290 return (std::fabs(fX - targetX) + std::fabs(fY - targetY)) < eps;
3291 }
3292 else if (auto curMacro = dynamic_cast<PlacementMacro *>(curPU))
3293 {

3299 {
3300 fY = (globalMaxY - 2 * eps) - curMacro->getTopOffset();
3301 }
3302 else if (fY + curMacro->getBottomOffset() < globalMinY + eps)
3303 {
3304 fY = (globalMinY + 2 * eps) - curMacro->getBottomOffset();
3305 }
3306
3307 if (fX + curMacro->getRightOffset() > globalMaxX - eps)
3308 {
3309 fX = (globalMaxX - 2 * eps) - curMacro->getRightOffset();
3310 }
3311 else if (fX + curMacro->getLeftOffset() < globalMinX + eps)
3312 {
3313 fX = (globalMinX + 2 * eps) - curMacro->getLeftOffset();
3314 }
3315 return (std::fabs(fX + offsetX - targetX) + std::fabs(fY + offsetY - targetY)) < eps;

3319 assert(false && "should not reach here");

3592 SharedBELTypeBinGrid[cellId2CellBinInfo[cellId].sharedTypeId][cellId2CellBinInfo[cellId].Y]
3593 [cellId2CellBinInfo[cellId].X]
3594 ->removeCell(designInfo->getCells()[cellId], cellId2CellBinInfo[cellId].occupation);
3595 SharedBELTypeBinGrid[cellId2CellBinInfo[cellId].sharedTypeId][binIdY][binIdX]->addCell(
3596 designInfo->getCells()[cellId], cellId2CellBinInfo[cellId].occupation);

3624 inline std::vector<DeviceInfo::DeviceSite *> *findNeiborSiteFromBinGrid(DesignInfo::DesignCell *curCell,
3625 float targetX, float targetY,
3626 float displacementThreshold,
3627 int siteNumThreshold)
3628 {
3629 // please note that the input DesignCell is only used to find the corresponding binGrid for site search.
3630 std::vector<DeviceInfo::DeviceSite *> *res = new std::vector<DeviceInfo::DeviceSite *>(0);
3631
3632 int binIdX, binIdY;
3633 getGridXY(targetX, targetY, binIdX, binIdY);
3634
3635 while (res->size() == 0)
3636 {
3637 auto sharedTypeIds = getPotentialBELTypeIDs(curCell->getCellType());
3638
3639 for (auto sharedTypeId : sharedTypeIds)
3640 {
3641 assert((unsigned int)curCell->getCellId() < cellId2CellBinInfo.size());
3642 assert(binIdY >= 0);
3643 assert((unsigned int)binIdY < SharedBELTypeBinGrid[sharedTypeId].size());
3644 assert(binIdX >= 0);
3645 assert((unsigned int)binIdX < SharedBELTypeBinGrid[sharedTypeId][binIdY].size());
3646
3647 std::vector<std::vector<PlacementBinInfo *>> &curBinGrid = SharedBELTypeBinGrid[sharedTypeId];
3648
3649 std::queue<std::pair<int, int>> binXYqueue;
3650 std::set<std::pair<int, int>> reachedBinXYs;
3651 binXYqueue.emplace(binIdX, binIdY);
3652 reachedBinXYs.emplace(binIdX, binIdY);
3653
3654 while (binXYqueue.size() > 0)
3655 {
3656 std::pair<int, int> curXY = binXYqueue.front();
3657 binXYqueue.pop();
3658 int curbinIdX = curXY.first, curbinIdY = curXY.second;
3659
3660 PlacementBinInfo *curBin = curBinGrid[curbinIdY][curbinIdX];
3661 float bin2TargetXYDistance = curBin->getManhattanDistanceTo(targetX, targetY);
3662 if (bin2TargetXYDistance > displacementThreshold)
3663 continue;
3664 int findSiteCnt = 0;
3665 for (auto curSite : curBin->getCorrespondingSites())
3666 {
3667 if (!curSite->isOccupied() && !curSite->isMapped())
3668 {
3669 if (getDisplacement(targetX, targetY, curSite) < displacementThreshold)
3670 {
3671 findSiteCnt++;
3672 res->push_back(curSite);
3673 }
3674 }
3675 }
3676
3677 if (res->size() < (unsigned int)siteNumThreshold)
3678 {
3679 for (int nextY = curbinIdY - 1; nextY <= curbinIdY + 1; nextY++)
3680 {
3681 for (int nextX = curbinIdX - 1; nextX <= curbinIdX + 1; nextX++)
3682 {
3683 if (!(nextY >= 0))
3684 continue;
3685 if (!((unsigned int)nextY < SharedBELTypeBinGrid[sharedTypeId].size()))
3686 continue;
3687 if (!(nextX >= 0))
3688 continue;
3689 if (!((unsigned int)nextX < SharedBELTypeBinGrid[sharedTypeId][binIdY].size()))
3690 continue;
3691 PlacementBinInfo *nextBin = curBinGrid[nextY][nextX];
3692 float nextBin2TargetXYDistance = nextBin->getManhattanDistanceTo(targetX, targetY);
3693 if (nextBin2TargetXYDistance > displacementThreshold)
3694 continue;
3695 std::pair<int, int> nextXY(nextX, nextY);
3696 if (reachedBinXYs.find(nextXY) == reachedBinXYs.end())
3697 {
3698 reachedBinXYs.insert(nextXY);
3699 binXYqueue.push(nextXY);
3700 }
3701 }
3702 }
3703 }
3704 }
3705 }
3706 displacementThreshold *= 1.5;
3707 }
3708
3709 return res;
3710 }

3946 inline unsigned int getPairPinNum(DesignInfo::DesignCell *LUTA, DesignInfo::DesignCell *LUTB)
3947 {
3948 if (LUTA->getInputPins().size() == 6 || LUTB->getInputPins().size() == 6 || LUTA->isLUT6() || LUTB->isLUT6())
3949 return 12;
3950
3951 int pinNumA = 0;
3952 int totalPin = 0;
3953 int netIds[5]; // be aware that a LUT might have pins connected to the same net and they should be treated as
3954 // different inputs.
3955
3956 for (auto tmpPin : LUTA->getInputPins())
3957 {
3958 if (!tmpPin->isUnconnected())
3959 {
3960 netIds[pinNumA] = tmpPin->getNet()->getElementIdInType();
3961 pinNumA++;
3962 }
3963 }
3964 totalPin = pinNumA;
3965 for (auto tmpPin : LUTB->getInputPins())
3966 {
3967 if (!tmpPin->isUnconnected())
3968 {
3969 bool matched = false;
3970 for (int i = 0; i < pinNumA; i++)
3971 {
3972 if (netIds[i] >= 0 && netIds[i] == tmpPin->getNet()->getElementIdInType())
3973 {
3974 netIds[i] = -1;
3975 matched = true;
3976 break;
3977 }
3978 }
3979 if (!matched)
3980 {
3981 totalPin++;
3982 }
3983 }
3984 }
3985 return totalPin;
3986 }
